      <title>南非总统拉马福萨将气候目标纳入法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-enshrines-climate-targets-into-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨签署了一项具有里程碑意义的法案，该法案将迫使各级政府在制定预算和决策时考虑气候因素。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/south-africa-s-ramaphosa-enshrines-climate-targets-into-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 12:32:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯有望在 2024 年大选中缩小特朗普的领先优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/kamala-harris-poised-to-cut-trump-s-lead-in-2024-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登决定放弃 2024 年白宫连任竞选，并支持卡马拉·哈里斯为继任者，这一决定对竞选产生了直接影响，以竞选捐款、预测市场和支持率来衡量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/kamala-harris-poised-to-cut-trump-s-lead-in-2024-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 12:27:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
