    <item>
      <title>印度政府注重就业 国防预算下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-defense-budget-drops-as-government-focuses-on-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度本财年的国防预算基本保持不变，但面对地区地缘政治动荡加剧，印度仍在增加军事装备方面的支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-defense-budget-drops-as-government-focuses-on-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 12:13:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
