    <item>
      <title>印度取消进口税以加速绿色能源的使用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-to-remove-import-taxes-to-speed-uptake-of-renewable-energy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度财政部长尼尔玛拉·西塔拉曼在预算演讲中表示，印度将取消 25 种关键矿产的进口税，并加大力度开发小型核反应堆，以加快采用清洁能源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/india-to-remove-import-taxes-to-speed-uptake-of-renewable-energy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:29:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪连任后首份预算案的赢家和输家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/who-gained-and-who-lost-in-modi-s-first-budget-after-reelection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是纳伦德拉·莫迪第三次当选总理以来印度的首份预算，重点是创造就业机会、支持本地企业和基础设施，而不会大幅增加赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/who-gained-and-who-lost-in-modi-s-first-budget-after-reelection</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 07:58:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪承诺提供 240 亿美元用于就业和向盟友提供经济援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/modi-pledges-24-billion-for-jobs-boosts-spending-to-allies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪承诺投入 2 万亿卢比（239 亿美元）来促进就业、改善印度的教育状况，增加对新盟友的支出，同时还设定了今年减少财政赤字的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/modi-pledges-24-billion-for-jobs-boosts-spending-to-allies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 06:05:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
